    <item>
      <title>自2023年以来销售后，腾讯加快AI的支出增长最快</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/tencent-grows-fastest-in-a-year-after-spate-of-holiday-game-hits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Tencent Holdings Ltd.概述了计划在自2023年以来的最快收入增长速度后，计划大幅提高AI基础设施支出的计划，这表明中国最有价值的公司打算打算在后Deepseek时代与竞争对手保持同步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/tencent-grows-fastest-in-a-year-after-spate-of-holiday-game-hits</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 08:37:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
